md:
giải nghĩa từ "industrial" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan và các từ trái nghĩa.

Industrial (adjective)

* Meaning: relating to industry or manufacturing
* Vietnamese: công nghiệp
* Example sentence: The industrial area is located on the outskirts of the city.
* Related words: industry, manufacturing, factory, production
* Antonyms: agricultural, commercial, residential

Industrial (noun)

* Meaning: a person who works in industry
* Vietnamese: người công nghiệp
* Example sentence: The industrial is responsible for ensuring the quality of the products.
* Related words: worker, employee, laborer, manufacturer
* Antonyms: farmer, merchant, resident

Note: The meaning of "industrial" can vary depending on the context in which it is used. In general, it refers to something related to industry or manufacturing.
